msgctxt "an6.89:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 6 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 6 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an6.89:0.2"
msgid "9. Sītivagga "
msgstr "9. Coolness "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an6.89:0.3"
msgid "89. Appahāyasutta "
msgstr "89. Not Giving Up "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.438, sc1
msgctxt "an6.89:1.1"
msgid "“Cha, bhikkhave, dhamme appahāya abhabbo diṭṭhisampadaṃ sacchikātuṃ. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, without giving up six things you can’t become accomplished in view. "

msgctxt "an6.89:1.2"
msgid "Katame cha? "
msgstr "What six? "

msgctxt "an6.89:1.3"
msgid "Sakkāyadiṭṭhiṃ, vicikicchaṃ, sīlabbataparāmāsaṃ, apāyagamanīyaṃ rāgaṃ, apāyagamanīyaṃ dosaṃ, apāyagamanīyaṃ mohaṃ. "
msgstr "Identity view, doubt, misapprehension of precepts and observances, and forms of greed, hate, and delusion that lead to rebirth in places of loss. "

msgctxt "an6.89:1.4"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, cha dhamme appahāya abhabbo diṭṭhisampadaṃ sacchikātuṃ. "
msgstr "Without giving up these six things you can’t become accomplished in view. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an6.89:2.1"
msgid "Cha, bhikkhave, dhamme pahāya bhabbo diṭṭhisampadaṃ sacchikātuṃ. "
msgstr "After giving up six things you can become accomplished in view. "

msgctxt "an6.89:2.2"
msgid "Katame cha? "
msgstr "What six? "

msgctxt "an6.89:2.3"
msgid "Sakkāyadiṭṭhiṃ, vicikicchaṃ, sīlabbataparāmāsaṃ, apāyagamanīyaṃ rāgaṃ, apāyagamanīyaṃ dosaṃ, apāyagamanīyaṃ mohaṃ. "
msgstr "Identity view, doubt, misapprehension of precepts and observances, and forms of greed, hate, and delusion that lead to rebirth in places of loss. "

msgctxt "an6.89:2.4"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, cha dhamme pahāya bhabbo diṭṭhisampadaṃ sacchikātun”ti. "
msgstr "After giving up these six things you can become accomplished in view.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an6.89:2.5"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

